Description: This is my final project for GIS 495
In my project I looked at how streamflow is correlated to water temperature, elevation, and wealth distribution

This location on the Oconaluftee in Birdtown, NC had no correlation coefficient between water temperature and streamflow. It has an elevation of 1843.25 and had an average streamflow of 771.5 in 2019. It is located in Swain County

This location on the Rocky near Siler City, NC had a correlation coefficient of -.15 between water temperature and streamflow. It has an elevation of 482.90 and had an average streamflow of 87.2 in 2019. It is located in Chatham County
